Cell["What age group tend to be our patients?", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"87ddeb91-4aa3-439f-b44a-26fc9cf7b3b3"],

Cell["How long have women and men been depressed? ", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"239f2ac6-c8d8-4ac8-a575-8851cb12ddb8"],

Cell["How long were their treatments: gender matters?", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"54e43214-eeca-46f9-ac08-3afd19249228"],

Cell["Depression with treatment recurred or not?", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"8cbf6e32-68ab-470b-98ac-cd6fb97cb8f9"],

Cell["\<\
Is there a correlation between the depression and treatment time? \
\>", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"e4661177-c189-4495-88b7-2dd196925265"],

Cell["What helped our patients: medication?", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"d0695265-e2e6-4d6a-881d-aa1633f5219a"],

Cell["Was our experiment design correct?", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"271e1f63-e89e-4ee2-b5d6-f8020f61a24b"]
