Cell["Importing and shaping data", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"b3049b4c-bf50-48ad-8c3a-dac3e966e13e"],

Cell["\<\
Data can be obtained from the study 

Prien et al. (1984). \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]Drug therapy in the prevention of \
recurrence in unipolar and bipolar affective disorders.\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] published in the Archives of General Psychiatry. \
This dataset is a famous subset of a clinical trial conducted by the National \
Institute of Mental Health (NIMH) called the \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]Collaborative Study of the Psychobiology of \
Depression.\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] The one we will work is a simplified \
dataset of the original. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.812756045784542*^9, 3.8127560583326683`*^9}, {
  3.8127561072485*^9, 3.812756107264786*^9}, {3.812756257383001*^9, 
