Cell["Training and test data set", "Title",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.814882383176199*^9, 
  3.8148823896857433`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"58949f37-b23c-473c-86e9-\
1cb58df3a517"],

Cell["\<\
Let us set up the Training Set for data composed by 80 patients (eliminating \
Hospital Column and first row for the Key names):\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.814878934960757*^9, 3.814878959179491*^9}, {
  3.8148822455219593`*^9, 
  3.8148822582257013`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"70a3f67e-feea-4c66-860f-\
529dbe049a27"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"TrainingData", "=", 
   RowBox[{"RandomSample", "[", 
    RowBox[{"assocDS", ",", "80"}], "]"}]}], ";"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.814878312706949*^9, 3.814878327892498*^9}, {
  3.8148788053673763`*^9, 3.814878814108329*^9}, {3.814878953631413*^9, 
  3.81487895389992*^9}, {3.814882226775577*^9, 3.81488223920695*^9}, {
  3.8429695890647283`*^9, 3.842969593094713*^9}},
 CellLabel->
  "In[940]:=",ExpressionUUID->"ae2bdf84-1d0f-4722-aed7-0dcb14755809"],

Cell["The test data are the remaining group : ", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8148789649100633`*^9, 
  3.814878973253916*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"76af641a-2465-47be-ac8f-\
e02695ee7919"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"TestData", "=", 
   RowBox[{"Complement", "[", 
    RowBox[{"assocDS", ",", "TrainingData"}], "]"}]}], ";"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.814878398620564*^9, 3.814878413524728*^9}, 
   3.8148788208174267`*^9, {3.8148822610815983`*^9, 3.8148822620005493`*^9}, {
   3.842969603200115*^9, 3.842969609103143*^9}},
 CellLabel->
  "In[941]:=",ExpressionUUID->"8628a8c5-2a16-4b1d-b8e6-06bf920b506f"],

Cell["\<\
Let us now organize the dataset in order to put into the model. For that we \
have to specify the classes that we want the model to predict. In this cases, \
the classes are defined by the Outcome: \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]Recurrence\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] or \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]No Recurrence\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]. 

Each class has now values which the model will be built upon. Since we want \
to predict recurrence or not, this information cannot be part of the unknown \
variables. So, we need to eliminate it from the values of the classes. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.814878978470121*^9, 3.814879007818913*^9}, {
   3.814879332966567*^9, 3.814879338844721*^9}, {3.814880293389185*^9, 
   3.814880319453281*^9}, {3.814880417117103*^9, 3.8148804261855173`*^9}, 
   3.842970531011503*^9},ExpressionUUID->"08a23d4b-8c8a-4c99-944f-\
e03a81c77ad1"],

Cell["\<\
Bellow None, None means that the output list is a nested list where the first \
level does not drop any row, the second level also does not drop any row, but \
the second column at level 2 is dropped . \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8446709576544247`*^9, 
  3.844670981227053*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"05070da4-ba6b-4ffd-9456-\
e7b9c03ead7a"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"GroupBy", "[", 
