Cell["\<\
We might further delete unknown variables that our analysis does not count as \
relevant for the predicted variable . Let us say that this is the case for \
the AccuteT . That can be decided when for example two variables are highly \
correlated, only 1 needs to be taken into consideration .  \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8429706588346453`*^9, 
  3.842970660356931*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"fd29e340-8aee-4388-abbb-\
5ae08164c8bf"],

