Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["ROC curve ", "Title",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9798079459022837`*^9, 
  3.979807948976309*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"bba19efc-7099-4a1e-82ae-\
6a3f72e6857b"],

Cell["\<\
False positive ratio (FPR), or false alarm, fall-out:  the ratio between the \
number of false positive (identified as positive when it is negative) and the \
total number of actual negative events (healthy people). You wish a small \
number.

Recall (or sensitivity): the ratio between the number of true positive \
(identified as positive when it is positive) and the total number of actual \
positive events (sick people). you wish a large number\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.907053335302219*^9, 3.907053339414214*^9}, {
   3.907053408635375*^9, 3.9070534260780773`*^9}, 3.907053458280277*^9, {
