Cell["\<\
Curve is created varying the threshold to which probabilities in [0, 1] are \
interpreted to be No Recurrence or Recurrence\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.979808168698086*^9, 
  3.979808203480548*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"e36abadf-e8ae-4594-950e-\
